y>seo_url<\/span>\" => \"<span class=sf-dump-str title=\"8 characters\">about-us<\/span>\"\n  \"<span class=sf-dump-key>templete<\/span>\" => \"<span class=sf-dump-str title=\"5 characters\">about<\/span>\"\n  \"<span class=sf-dump-key>publish<\/span>\" => \"<span class=sf-dump-str title=\"9 characters\">published<\/span>\"\n  \"<span class=sf-dump-key>is_parent<\/span>\" => <span class=sf-dump-const>null<\/span>\n  \"<span class=sf-dump-key>description<\/span>\" => \"<span class=sf-dump-str title=\"51 characters\">We help companies and candidates find the right fit<\/span>\"\n  \"<span class=sf-dump-key>shortDescription<\/span>\" => \"\"\"\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"1260 characters\">&lt;h3&gt;About&amp;nbsp;VoteYour&lt;\/h3&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"1260 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"1260 characters\">&lt;p&gt;Welcome to VoteYour &amp;ndash; a platform designed to amplify your voice and make your opinions matter. We believe that every vote counts and that collective decisions can shape the future. Together, we can spark meaningful conversations that drive positive change.&lt;\/p&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"1260 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n<\/span><\/span>\n    <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"1260 characters\">&lt;p&gt;With VoteYour, you can participate in real-time polls on trending topics, create your own polls, and engage in discussions that reflect your interests. Whether it&amp;rsquo;s politics, entertainment, lifestyle, or social issues, VoteYour lets you explore diverse perspectives while staying completely anonymous. You&amp;rsquo;ll also have access to real-time poll results, helping you stay informed about public opinions.&lt;\/p&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns